"https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-here-comes-the-pain-25th-anniversary-us-tour-with-knocked-loose-buy-tickets-3752450">宣布了与 Knocked Loose 等乐队的“Here Comes The Pain”25 周年美国巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eloy-casagrande-explains-complicated-decision-to-leave-sepultura-for-slipknot-3755878">Eloy Casagrande 解释离开 Sepultura 加入 Slipknot 的“复杂”决定的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
